No. 10-7845. Eric Vasquez, Petitioner v. United States. 562 U.S. 1170, 131 S. Ct. 972,

178 L. Ed. 2d 806,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 73. January 10, 2011.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit denied.
